1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,700
=Episode 9=

16
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,719
Tell me the truth.

17
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:52,640
Did you take the title deed?

18
00:01:54,159 --> 00:01:54,959
Yes.

19
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,000
Why?

20
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,959
Why would you do such a thing?

21
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:03,840
The title deed belonged to Mr. Xu.

22
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:06,000
Mr. Xu was perfectly willing

23
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,439
to change the name with me.

24
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:10,879
If you want to interrogate someone,
go ask your husband.

25
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:23,400
What on earth do we owe you?

26
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,960
I gave birth to you and raised you.

27
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,120
What did I do wrong

28
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,639
to make you treat me like this?

29
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,240
You tell me, Bai Xia.

30
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,759
I was doing just fine.

31
00:02:34,950 --> 00:02:36,879
You're the one
who forced your way into my life

32
00:02:36,879 --> 00:02:38,360
and dragged me into this mess,

33
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:40,800
dragging me from house to house
and living a miserable life

34
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,960
like a parasite.

35
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:47,960
Bai Xia,

36
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:50,599
(23 years ago)
the one who started all of this was you.

37
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,520
You were the one who snatched me

38
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,439
away from my father.

39
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,080
Liangliang.

40
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:02,840
Liangliang.

41
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:05,840
Liangliang,

42
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,479
come home with me.

43
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:07,919
Be gentle.

44
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:08,639
No.

45
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:09,520
Come home with me.

46
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,599
She still doesn't know anything.

47
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,400
Dad!

48
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:13,199
Liangliang, come home with me.

49
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,639
Dad!

50
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,199
Dad!

51
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:19,400
Liangliang!

52
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,800
Dad!

53
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,360
She still doesn't know anything!

54
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:25,879
Liangliang.

55
00:03:43,919 --> 00:03:46,240
After you graduated from university,
you made me promise

56
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,719
not to interfere with you anymore

57
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,319
and not to come looking for you.

58
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,319
I promised you,

59
00:03:53,159 --> 00:03:54,400
and I kept my word.

60
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:57,280
I never mentioned you to anyone again.

61
00:03:58,759 --> 00:04:00,159
But what have you done?

62
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:02,400
How could you treat me like this?

63
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,599
What have I done?

64
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,039
Bai Xia,

65
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,120
the money on this card

66
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:13,680
is enough for you to buy
three No. 88 Linwei Alleys.

67
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,719
Take this card,

68
00:04:14,719 --> 00:04:16,480
take Mr. Xu, and leave this place.

69
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:17,759
Leave this city.

70
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:19,160
Leave my life.

71
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,040
And never come back.

72
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:32,639
Bai Liangliang.

73
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:33,879
Bai Liangliang!

74
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,519
Take your money.

75
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,959
I don't need your charity.

76
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,399
I know.

77
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,000
Deep down, you look down on me.

78
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:54,199
You're unwilling to admit
my relationship with Mr. Xu.

79
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:58,639
Don't worry.

80
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,920
We won't involve you.

81
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,680
I'm moving out.

82
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:06,120
I have the ability to let Mr. Xu

83
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,360
and me live a good life.

84
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:48,540
(Salted Duck)

85
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,360
She made Chen Xi refuse my funding.

86
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,160
In the office,

87
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,519
she gave me a piece of her mind.

88
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,800
Alright, our boss helped you

89
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,879
hit back, right?

90
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,639
When I walked out of the company

91
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,800
and saw those five cars parked there,

92
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,079
I was completely stunned.

93
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:09,319
It's already come to that.

94
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:10,480
I think what we did

95
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,600
was actually very passionate.

96
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,000
Right?

97
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,879
Come on, cheers.

98
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:14,000
Come. To passion, cheers!

99
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:18,319
I'm not trying to be a wet blanket,
but a whim won't last long.

100
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:19,319
Rao Yuci,

101
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,360
Lysen is so big,

102
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:24,920
you could have gone
to a much better department.

103
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,480
Why did you

104
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:28,720
insist on

105
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,759
choosing ours?

106
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,319
You guys are the best.

107
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,720
And I believe you

108
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,879
can lead us, Mr. Yu.

109
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:40,040
The way you said that

110
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,800
is a bit too "official."

111
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:46,240
Someone once told me

112
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:47,600
that, facing this

113
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,199
increasingly crazy world,

114
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:54,040
if there's someone who wants
to make a small change,

115
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,879
and if you meet such a person,

116
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,439
they must be a friend.

117
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,680
I think some people nowadays

118
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,560
treat life like a game,

119
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:04,879
and money is

120
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,040
the ultimate reward.

121
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:09,040
I think for us,

122
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,360
the most fortunate

123
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,040
and most important thing is

124
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:16,920
that we still have
a bit of our ideals left.

125
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:19,720
Do we really want

126
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,759
to just go with the flow?

127
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,920
Do we want to compromise

128
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,959
for this game?

129
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:24,580
(Investment Dept 3)

130
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,959
Actually, we do have a choice.

131
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:29,480
Our choice

132
00:07:29,759 --> 00:07:32,720
is to stay true
to our original intentions.

133
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:36,639
You are the few normal people

134
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:40,079
I've met at Lysen Group.

135
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:43,480
You've also made me feel

136
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,160
a long-lost sense of humanity.

137
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,040
Before, I might not have understood
you that well.

138
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,800
If we face any storms in the future,

139
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:01,120
let's face them together.

140
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,120
To humanity.

141
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:09,290
- To humanity.
- To humanity.

142
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:19,399
No. 88 Linwei Alley is the most difficult
household to deal with

143
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,800
in the Urban Renewal Project.

144
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,279
Without this household's consent,

145
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:25,720
the other households won't agree either.

146
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:33,940
(Property Ownership Certificate
of the People's Republic of China)

147
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:37,919
These are the title deeds
for No. 88 Linwei Alley

148
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,960
and the ten nearby shops.

149
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,759
As for the remaining 70 percent,

150
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:46,180
I can help you
get them all settled, too.

151
00:08:51,180 --> 00:08:53,900
(Owner: Bai Liangliang)

152
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:08,360
To me,

153
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,360
No. 88 Linwei Alley

154
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,559
isn't just a piece of land.

155
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:15,200
It's my past.

156
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,960
Now,

157
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,159
I'm erasing my past

158
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,480
and handing it over to you, Mr. Jiang.

159
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,679
I'm doing this

160
00:09:28,399 --> 00:09:29,559
only because I hope you

161
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:31,000
can see my sincerity

162
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:33,120
and give me an opportunity.

163
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,200
Have you eaten?

164
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:50,679
Boss,

165
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,790
another order of fried rice noodles.

166
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:53,879
Coming right up.

167
00:09:58,519 --> 00:09:59,639
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

168
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:27,919
Ms. Bai Xia, what's wrong?

169
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,320
The house is gone.

170
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,879
What happened?

171
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:54,840
My house is gone.

172
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,679
Mr. Xu...

173
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,000
The house is gone.

174
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,879
Ms. Bai,

175
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,919
the house won't be gone.

176
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,200
I'll help you find a way.

177
00:11:28,159 --> 00:11:29,360
I know that acquiring Bosi

178
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,780
has always been a very important plan
of yours, Mr. Jiang.

179
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,200
But Yang Jinwan

180
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,840
has never made his stance clear.

181
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,080
Yang Jinwan is the helmsman of Bosi.

182
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,080
This attitude of his is suspicious.

183
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:41,360
I was thinking

184
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,039
the Urban Project

185
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:45,480
is likely just a facade.

186
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,879
To prevent the acquisition,

187
00:11:48,279 --> 00:11:50,080
he wants you to keep thinking

188
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:52,039
that Bosi is just the same as always.

189
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,399
So, from the very beginning,

190
00:11:58,039 --> 00:12:00,600
the people at Bosi didn't care
about the Urban Project at all.

191
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,320
You've seen the report too.

192
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,639
Apart from real estate,

193
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,120
Bosi has clearly

194
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:08,759
already found other things
they are interested in.

195
00:12:14,340 --> 00:12:17,100
(Investigation Report
on Green Building Materials Companies)

196
00:12:25,860 --> 00:12:28,200
The building materials companies
that Bosi wants to acquire

197
00:12:28,690 --> 00:12:30,240
are their real path to transformation.

198
00:12:35,350 --> 00:12:38,440
To do renovations on existing buildings,
one must use green building materials.

199
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,559
On this list,

200
00:12:40,559 --> 00:12:42,200
every single company they want to buy

201
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,000
is related to

202
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,240
green building materials.

203
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:47,320
This is what Yang Jinwan values right now.

204
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,559
This is also the best way for Bosi

205
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,960
to break through and develop.

206
00:12:51,759 --> 00:12:52,759
But if you, Mr. Jiang,

207
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:53,879
stay one step ahead of them

208
00:12:54,279 --> 00:12:55,480
and hold their cards,

209
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:58,000
then the bargaining power
for acquiring Bosi

210
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,360
will be in your hands.

211
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:02,519
As for the houses

212
00:13:02,519 --> 00:13:03,919
that Bai Liangliang acquired,

213
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:05,960
they are not important.

214
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,320
It's fine.

215
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:09,759
Thank you.

216
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,279
Thank you.

217
00:13:11,799 --> 00:13:12,639
Mr. Jiang,

218
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,120
we can meet now.

219
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:19,679
- Liangliang.
- Mr. Rao.

220
00:13:21,540 --> 00:13:22,799
(Shanghai Real Estate
Purchase and Sale Contract)

221
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,120
They're all signed.

222
00:13:25,039 --> 00:13:27,039
The rest is up to you.

223
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,600
Don't worry, Mr. Rao.

224
00:13:28,610 --> 00:13:29,990
There definitely won't be any problem.

225
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,159
Mr. Jiang.

226
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:50,800
Regarding the follow-up
with the merchants, it's all settled.

227
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:52,559
These are all the remaining title deeds.

228
00:13:53,399 --> 00:13:54,120
This is my gift

229
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,320
to you, Mr. Jiang.

230
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,039
I hope

231
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:58,600
you can let me return to Lysen

232
00:13:58,879 --> 00:14:00,080
to continue serving you.

233
00:14:06,879 --> 00:14:07,679
This land...

234
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:11,480
Neither Lysen nor I need it anymore.

235
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,120
What do you mean?

236
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,639
You're a step too late.

237
00:14:20,399 --> 00:14:21,759
You've lost to Rao Yuci again.

238
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,279
I hope this time,

239
00:14:29,279 --> 00:14:30,679
you didn't spend too much.

240
00:14:31,799 --> 00:14:33,240
I warned you long ago

241
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:35,159
not to try to second-guess others.

242
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:37,000
Especially you,

243
00:14:37,039 --> 00:14:37,879
Bai Liangliang.

244
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:42,120
Why do you always want
to be the one waiting to swoop in?

245
00:15:02,660 --> 00:15:04,180
(Uncle Rao)

246
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:12,580
(Uncle Rao)

247
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,759
Hello?

248
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,240
Mr. Rao.

249
00:15:24,759 --> 00:15:26,639
(It was all for nothing.)

250
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,279
(Bai Liangliang,)

251
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,279
(your token of loyalty)

252
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,679
(is just a pile of scrap paper.)

253
00:15:39,679 --> 00:15:40,480
Come on in.

254
00:15:43,559 --> 00:15:44,360
Mr. Jiang.

255
00:15:45,399 --> 00:15:46,960
Are Ren Jing and the finance and legal

256
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,000
ready?

257
00:15:48,759 --> 00:15:49,759
They're all ready.

258
00:15:51,039 --> 00:15:52,000
Tell them to move.

259
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,360
Yes, Mr. Jiang.

260
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:57,200
We were doing just fine.

261
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,200
Why is this happening?

262
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,120
Colleagues from Dept 2,

263
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,080
please calm down.

264
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:00,960
I repeat.

265
00:16:01,279 --> 00:16:02,480
Hand over all materials

266
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:04,240
related to the Linwei Alley Urban Project.

267
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,200
What's going on?

268
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,399
Ms. Chen,

269
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,559
Ms. Ren requested the transfer
of all materials

270
00:16:12,559 --> 00:16:13,690
for the Linwei Alley Urban Project.

271
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,159
Ms. Ren,

272
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:16,480
who gave HR

273
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:19,039
the permission to meddle
in Investment Dept 2's business?

274
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,960
This isn't within your scope of duties.

275
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,240
Mr. Jiang

276
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:23,759
directly ordered us to do this.

277
00:16:24,679 --> 00:16:25,480
Ms. Chen,

278
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,559
if you have any objections,

279
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,120
you can take them up with Mr. Jiang.

280
00:16:30,519 --> 00:16:31,279
If anyone in Dept 2

281
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:32,039
doesn't cooperate,

282
00:16:32,039 --> 00:16:33,519
we'll handle it per company policy.

283
00:16:33,639 --> 00:16:34,440
- Yes.
- Yes.

284
00:16:46,759 --> 00:16:47,559
Ms. Chen.

285
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,639
Ms. Chen!

286
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,440
Get out of the way.

287
00:16:51,559 --> 00:16:52,799
I need to see Mr. Jiang.

288
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:53,960
I'm sorry, Ms. Chen.

289
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,800
Mr. Jiang is not seeing
anyone this morning.

290
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:56,960
Mr. Jiang!

291
00:16:57,600 --> 00:17:00,000
My Dept 2 clearly created
the Linwei Alley Urban Project.

292
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,200
Why stop it now?

293
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:02,759
Mr. Jiang!

294
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,440
Why on earth is this happening?

295
00:17:05,319 --> 00:17:06,559
Stop making a scene.

296
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,000
Ms. Chen,

297
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,119
Mr. Jiang's decision

298
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:10,359
will not be changed.

299
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:20,480
Mr. Pengyu.

300
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,750
This is the budget for the contracts
with the Snack Street merchants.

301
00:17:29,039 --> 00:17:29,880
Tell finance

302
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,960
to have the funds ready.

303
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:31,839
If needed,

304
00:17:31,839 --> 00:17:32,920
I'll notify you at any time.

305
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,799
Alright.

306
00:17:58,500 --> 00:17:59,279
Someone's in the elevator.

307
00:17:59,279 --> 00:17:59,960
Ms. Chen.

308
00:18:03,799 --> 00:18:04,599
Rao Yuci,

309
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,960
do you think what you're doing is funny?

310
00:18:09,210 --> 00:18:11,599
The whole company knows where I've been
for the past three years.

311
00:18:11,599 --> 00:18:12,640
Don't tell me you don't.

312
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:16,359
I think I also know
what you did behind the scenes

313
00:18:16,359 --> 00:18:18,000
when the Snack Street was moving.

314
00:18:18,519 --> 00:18:19,990
If we're talking about that, Chen Xi,

315
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,380
you don't seem to know the rules either.

316
00:18:25,039 --> 00:18:26,039
I'm sorry.

317
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:27,920
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

318
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,480
Then, let me be clearer.

319
00:18:30,119 --> 00:18:31,880
Know your place,

320
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,680
and know who I am.

321
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:36,000
You couldn't even beat Bai Liangliang.

322
00:18:37,119 --> 00:18:38,599
And you want to be my rival?

323
00:18:41,759 --> 00:18:43,039
- Mr. Jiang.
- Mr. Jiang.

324
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,160
Good morning, Mr. Jiang.

325
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,400
Find some time to buy new clothes.

326
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,359
Dress yourself up.

327
00:19:09,319 --> 00:19:10,319
If you go out like this,

328
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:11,599
people will think

329
00:19:11,599 --> 00:19:13,790
there's something wrong
with Lysen's salary conditions.

330
00:19:14,119 --> 00:19:15,720
I'm used to this, Mr. Jiang.

331
00:19:17,759 --> 00:19:20,519
The Snack Street Renewal Plan
is about to start its trial opening.

332
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,440
Dept 3 has worked hard.

333
00:19:24,039 --> 00:19:24,880
No problem.

334
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,240
I'm here.

335
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:29,450
I'll head out first, Mr. Jiang.

336
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,920
I wonder how this soft opening is going.

337
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:40,960
Now

338
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,960
is the moment to witness
the fruits of our labor.

339
00:19:43,839 --> 00:19:46,160
Dept 3 is currently the laughingstock
of the company.

340
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:46,960
You know,

341
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:48,200
I've already

342
00:19:48,279 --> 00:19:49,799
prepared myself to be humiliated today.

343
00:19:53,279 --> 00:19:54,079
Wait.

344
00:19:54,559 --> 00:19:55,359
You...

345
00:19:55,799 --> 00:19:57,200
What's with all this darkness?

346
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,720
Are you sure it's today?

347
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,240
Wang.

348
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:09,230
Didn't we agree that the lights only go on
after I finish speaking?

349
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:10,960
I got a little ahead of myself.

350
00:20:11,079 --> 00:20:12,240
My apologies, my apologies.

351
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:13,039
Sorry about that.

352
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:15,440
This actually looks good.

353
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,359
I was just anxious.

354
00:20:16,519 --> 00:20:17,599
My fault, my fault.

355
00:20:17,839 --> 00:20:18,799
My bad.

356
00:20:23,759 --> 00:20:24,759
Everyone's here.

357
00:20:25,119 --> 00:20:27,359
Please join us in welcoming everyone to

358
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:30,480
- Linwei Alley in our memories!
- Linwei Alley in our memories!

359
00:20:31,079 --> 00:20:32,359
Great! Welcome!

360
00:20:34,039 --> 00:20:35,000
This indoor market

361
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,240
is such a successful recreation.

362
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:38,060
Even though it's inside
a commercial building,

363
00:20:38,079 --> 00:20:39,279
every table and chair,

364
00:20:39,359 --> 00:20:42,440
every sign and shelf, perfectly captures
the feeling of a roadside stall.

365
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,319
Yuci's creative idea is brilliant.

366
00:20:56,279 --> 00:20:57,319
Thank you.

367
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:59,880
Welcome to Linwei Alley.

368
00:21:03,519 --> 00:21:04,319
Rao.

369
00:21:04,559 --> 00:21:05,359
Rao,

370
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,640
come and eat with us.

371
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,400
We have plenty.

372
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,680
Just worry about yourself.

373
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,319
Come, try this.

374
00:21:11,319 --> 00:21:12,440
You're too kind.

375
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:14,079
Osmanthus mixed fruit bowl.

376
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:15,780
Feel free to give more feedback.

377
00:21:15,799 --> 00:21:16,839
I'll give feedback, no problem.

378
00:21:16,839 --> 00:21:18,480
Well, don't charge us.

379
00:21:18,759 --> 00:21:20,559
It's on the house. Today is my treat.

380
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,400
Ma'am, you must charge us.

381
00:21:22,839 --> 00:21:24,599
What's wrong with you?
Don't be so cheap!

382
00:21:24,599 --> 00:21:25,119
What are you doing?

383
00:21:25,119 --> 00:21:26,000
The boss said it's free.

384
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:27,559
Boss, Sima Yang will have to pay today.

385
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,680
It's the owner's treat,

386
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:32,240
but we'll deduct it
from Sima Yang's salary.

387
00:21:32,359 --> 00:21:33,160
Exactly!

388
00:21:34,079 --> 00:21:35,200
Thanks, Sima Yang.

389
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:38,079
You should smile more.

390
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:41,720
The way you're smiling today
is a bit different than before.

391
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:47,720
Wait.

392
00:21:47,759 --> 00:21:49,720
Yuci, let's take a photo.

393
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,960
All of us from Dept 3 together.

394
00:21:52,079 --> 00:21:54,559
Come on, this angle is perfect.

395
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,720
Everyone from Dept 3!

396
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:57,599
Three,

397
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:58,720
two,

398
00:21:59,000 --> 00:21:59,799
one.

399
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:00,920
- Keep it up!
- Keep it up!

400
00:22:23,559 --> 00:22:24,400
I'm not in the mood.

401
00:22:26,759 --> 00:22:29,759
Ms. Bai, you look beautiful
even when you're angry.

402
00:22:31,839 --> 00:22:32,680
Don't be upset.

403
00:22:32,690 --> 00:22:34,260
It's not like
it's your money being lost.

404
00:22:34,279 --> 00:22:35,880
Is this about the money?

405
00:22:36,279 --> 00:22:39,000
Rao Yuci completely ruined
my plan to return to Lysen Group.

406
00:22:40,559 --> 00:22:41,279
Well, if you

407
00:22:41,279 --> 00:22:42,640
had told me your plan earlier,

408
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:44,200
maybe I could have been of some help.

409
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:47,119
But it's too late for that now.

410
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:50,519
That's why we

411
00:22:51,500 --> 00:22:52,440
need to help each other.

412
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:57,200
Bai Muran.

413
00:22:59,319 --> 00:23:00,119
Pengyu.

414
00:23:00,559 --> 00:23:01,640
Long time no see.

415
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:02,160
Yeah.

416
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:03,319
So long that you've forgotten me, right?

417
00:23:03,319 --> 00:23:03,640
No.

418
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:06,120
I was wondering why you disappeared
as soon as you got back.

419
00:23:06,240 --> 00:23:07,079
Turns out

420
00:23:07,079 --> 00:23:09,319
you were here playing golf
with such a beautiful lady.

421
00:23:09,319 --> 00:23:10,119
Don't talk nonsense.

422
00:23:10,119 --> 00:23:10,960
This is my girlfriend.

423
00:23:11,640 --> 00:23:12,319
Liangliang,

424
00:23:12,319 --> 00:23:13,200
let me introduce you.

425
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:14,519
This is Mr. Pengyu of Yuanjian Capital.

426
00:23:14,519 --> 00:23:15,960
We went to high school
together in Australia.

427
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:17,000
We're childhood friends.

428
00:23:17,559 --> 00:23:18,359
Nice to meet you.

429
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,000
Hello.

430
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:22,240
Xu Ning and the others are here too.

431
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,319
Go say hello in a bit.

432
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:24,240
Sure, I'll head over soon.

433
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,039
I won't keep you.

434
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:30,480
Are you two very close?

435
00:23:32,559 --> 00:23:34,119
Back in Australia, we were quite close.

436
00:23:34,559 --> 00:23:36,400
This kid only cares about having fun.

437
00:23:37,119 --> 00:23:38,440
He never takes anything seriously.

438
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:56,500
(Xian Pengyu: 1307)

439
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,119
Where are you going later?

440
00:24:01,359 --> 00:24:02,759
I'm going shopping.

441
00:24:03,119 --> 00:24:05,640
I'm going to spend
all my hard-earned money.

442
00:24:05,799 --> 00:24:07,200
I need to enjoy life.

443
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:09,500
Otherwise, how will I have
the motivation to earn more?

444
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,880
Don't worry too much

445
00:24:18,260 --> 00:24:19,640
about those houses in Linwei Alley.

446
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:20,960
I know.

447
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:25,359
Liangliang, if you have time
in a couple of days,

448
00:24:25,359 --> 00:24:26,319
let's invite Bai Muran.

449
00:24:26,319 --> 00:24:27,279
The three of us

450
00:24:27,759 --> 00:24:28,880
should have dinner together.

451
00:24:30,759 --> 00:24:32,039
What do you want to say to him?

452
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,160
Tell him

453
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:37,079
that his girlfriend is sleeping
with you behind his back?

454
00:24:37,759 --> 00:24:39,720
Or tell him that I plan to give him up,

455
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,000
the heir to Baiye,

456
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,160
to be with you?

457
00:24:42,559 --> 00:24:43,599
Would he believe that?

458
00:24:45,599 --> 00:24:46,920
I was just joking.

459
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:49,319
Do you have to be so blunt?

460
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:52,480
You knew what kind of person
I was when we first met.

461
00:24:53,359 --> 00:24:54,160
True.

462
00:24:55,279 --> 00:24:56,079
I know

463
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,200
that in your heart,

464
00:24:57,559 --> 00:24:58,599
he and I are the same.

465
00:24:59,519 --> 00:25:01,720
Two of a kind, birds of a feather.

466
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,960
I rely on my mother,

467
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,839
and he relies on his grandmother.

468
00:25:12,079 --> 00:25:13,160
What did you just say?

469
00:25:14,319 --> 00:25:15,119
Two of a kind.

470
00:25:15,359 --> 00:25:16,400
Birds of a feather.

471
00:25:17,079 --> 00:25:17,880
The next sentence.

472
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:21,640
I rely on my mother,

473
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:24,039
and he relies on his grandmother.

474
00:25:26,799 --> 00:25:28,000
You're a bit better than him.

475
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,039
Care to elaborate?

476
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:33,319
At least you reminded me

477
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:35,559
it's time for me to find the person

478
00:25:35,559 --> 00:25:37,440
who can help me return to Lysen.

479
00:25:38,799 --> 00:25:39,920
I'm off. See you.

480
00:25:46,860 --> 00:25:49,340
(Baiyun Art Gallery)

481
00:25:52,359 --> 00:25:54,359
Madam, the auspicious time is near.

482
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:56,980
(Bai Qingyu, Chairman of Baiye Group)

483
00:26:01,039 --> 00:26:02,359
Are you rushing me?

484
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:06,319
Didn't I say?

485
00:26:07,319 --> 00:26:09,960
The scissors must
have a phoenix on them.

486
00:26:14,519 --> 00:26:15,319
Grandmother.

487
00:26:16,799 --> 00:26:17,599
Liangliang.

488
00:26:18,279 --> 00:26:19,920
Come, come on in.

489
00:26:22,759 --> 00:26:23,559
Grandmother.

490
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:26,279
Muran

491
00:26:26,279 --> 00:26:27,440
is really something.

492
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:29,799
He's back, yet he's nowhere to be seen.

493
00:26:31,039 --> 00:26:32,480
Muran is busy with work.

494
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:33,559
He sent me instead.

495
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:35,960
I specially selected
a pair of scissors for you.

496
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:37,319
Take a look.

497
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:39,160
Are they suitable?

498
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,319
These are the ones.

499
00:26:54,279 --> 00:26:55,920
Let's head over.

500
00:26:57,119 --> 00:26:58,400
Welcome, everyone.

501
00:26:58,400 --> 00:26:59,319
Thank you for attending

502
00:26:59,319 --> 00:27:00,839
the opening ceremony

503
00:27:00,839 --> 00:27:02,480
of Baiye Group's art gallery.

504
00:27:03,119 --> 00:27:04,960
The works on display today

505
00:27:05,839 --> 00:27:08,160
are from the private collection

506
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,400
of my late husband and me.

507
00:27:09,759 --> 00:27:10,880
That we can all

508
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:11,960
gather here today

509
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,960
is a rare and wonderful occasion.

510
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,519
Thank you, everyone!

511
00:27:24,759 --> 00:27:25,680
I declare

512
00:27:25,839 --> 00:27:28,480
Baiyun Art Gallery officially open!

513
00:27:33,559 --> 00:27:34,359
So,

514
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,720
has work been going well lately?

515
00:27:38,559 --> 00:27:39,880
There's been a slight setback.

516
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,599
Mr. Jiang feels

517
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:45,240
that I should take a break.

518
00:27:49,079 --> 00:27:51,000
Regarding the Dada Wine Industry matter,

519
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:53,519
there were issues with both
the analysts and the project.

520
00:27:54,039 --> 00:27:55,640
It's inconvenient for Mr. Jiang

521
00:27:55,839 --> 00:27:57,279
to take the blame personally,

522
00:27:57,759 --> 00:27:59,000
so someone

523
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,880
has to share the burden for him.

524
00:28:03,759 --> 00:28:04,839
Has Jiang Dongchao

525
00:28:04,839 --> 00:28:06,519
lost his mind?

526
00:28:07,079 --> 00:28:08,400
Has he forgotten

527
00:28:09,039 --> 00:28:11,440
that not only
does Muran represent our family,

528
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:14,079
but you also represent the Bai family?

529
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,759
What is he doing?

530
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:21,519
Trying to sideline
the Bai family so soon?

531
00:28:22,839 --> 00:28:23,640
Grandmother,

532
00:28:24,039 --> 00:28:26,799
perhaps you've misunderstood Mr. Jiang.

533
00:28:27,279 --> 00:28:28,599
You are his teacher.

534
00:28:28,599 --> 00:28:29,880
He always remembers that.

535
00:28:30,240 --> 00:28:31,480
It's just that Mr. Jiang

536
00:28:33,079 --> 00:28:35,079
has more and more people around him now,

537
00:28:35,319 --> 00:28:36,400
and they're a mixed bunch.

538
00:28:37,079 --> 00:28:38,599
I'm not sure if these people

539
00:28:39,319 --> 00:28:40,759
will affect the relationship

540
00:28:40,759 --> 00:28:42,319
between Mr. Jiang and the Bai family

541
00:28:42,559 --> 00:28:43,799
in the future.

542
00:28:57,319 --> 00:28:58,559
Dr. Chen, sorry to trouble you

543
00:28:58,559 --> 00:28:59,680
to make the trip here.

544
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,440
Not at all.

545
00:29:01,599 --> 00:29:04,000
This is the gift voucher
Lysen prepares for our clients.

546
00:29:04,359 --> 00:29:05,920
Thank you for the assessment last time.

547
00:29:06,799 --> 00:29:07,640
Thank you, Ms. Ren.

548
00:29:10,319 --> 00:29:11,119
Dr. Chen,

549
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,799
there's something I want to ask.

550
00:29:14,559 --> 00:29:15,359
Please, go ahead.

551
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,319
This time,

552
00:29:17,759 --> 00:29:19,400
were you intentionally helping Rao Yuci?

553
00:29:25,260 --> 00:29:26,720
Why do you ask that all of a sudden?

554
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,400
If you really were helping her,

555
00:29:34,900 --> 00:29:37,000
then I'd have to question
the authenticity and accuracy

556
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,200
of this assessment.

557
00:29:39,559 --> 00:29:40,359
Ms. Ren,

558
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:45,519
on this matter, you don't need
to question my professionalism.

559
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,440
What should we eat?

560
00:29:49,839 --> 00:29:50,759
What to eat?

561
00:29:50,799 --> 00:29:52,000
The boss is asking what to eat.

562
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:53,519
Since you're treating,
shouldn't we have something nice?

563
