As soon as I enter
the restaurant, I'll be like...

574
00:30:09,319 --> 00:30:10,039
I'll be like, I'll be like...

575
00:30:10,039 --> 00:30:11,720
I'll be like, "Hello"
and get active.

576
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:13,480
Tian Tian, you need to say "salut" too.

577
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:15,240
Salut, salut!

578
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,839
Hello, hello!

579
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:17,720
Salut, salut!

580
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:18,580
That's how it's done.

581
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:19,680
Rao Yuci!

582
00:30:23,519 --> 00:30:24,559
What are you doing?

583
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:25,720
Why are you hitting people?

584
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:26,319
What's going on?

585
00:30:26,319 --> 00:30:27,079
Who are you?

586
00:30:27,100 --> 00:30:27,839
What's going on?

587
00:30:27,839 --> 00:30:28,920
Why are you hitting her?

588
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:29,960
