596
00:30:37,079 --> 00:30:37,799
Security!

597
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:38,599
Why are you hitting people?

598
00:30:38,599 --> 00:30:39,079
Rao Yuci!

599
00:30:39,079 --> 00:30:39,880
