602
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:43,519
Let go of me!

603
00:30:43,599 --> 00:30:44,400
Let go!

604
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:46,480
From the time you were little,
all you've ever brought me

605
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:47,720
- is bad luck.
- Are you okay?

606
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:48,680
Mr. Yu,

607
00:30:50,759 --> 00:30:51,799
